languages.text: "Ну, вот и все, славная охота была! Мне по душе пришлось биться вместе с тобой, новеньк{mf|ий|ая}. Ты заслужил{mf||а} сувенир за свое усердие. Вортен, награди {mf|его|ее}!"
"This has been a fine hunt! I have enjoyed fighting together, new blood. You deserve something good for your efforts. Worten, reward {mf|him|her}!"

languages.text: «¡Ha sido una buena cacería! He disfrutado luchando junto a usted, {mf|novato|novata}. Se merece un premio a sus esfuerzos. ¡Worten, recompénsa{mf|lo|la}!».
languages.original_text: "This has been a fine hunt! I have enjoyed fighting together, new blood. You deserve something good for your efforts. Worten, reward {mf|him|her}!"

traits.locale_text: «¡Bueno, la cacería fue divertida mientras duró! He disfrutado luchando junto a usted, {mf|novato|novata}. Se merece un recuerdo por su participación. ¡Worten, recompénsa{mf|lo|la}!».

languages.text: “真是场不错的狩猎！我喜欢和你一起战斗，新来的。你干得很不错，值得好好奖励。沃尔腾，奖励{mf|他|她}吧！”
languages.original_text: "This has been a fine hunt! I have enjoyed fighting together, new blood. You deserve something good for your efforts. Worten, reward {mf|him|her}!"

traits.locale_text: “嗯，打猎的时候总是很有趣！我喜欢和你一起战斗，新来的。你干得很不错，值得嘉奖。沃尔腾，奖励{mf|他|她}吧！”

languages.text: « Ce fut une bien belle chasse ! J'ai passé un bon moment à combattre à vos côtés, novice. Vous méritez un petit quelque chose pour vos efforts. Worten, récompense-{mf|le|la} ! »
languages.original_text: "This has been a fine hunt! I have enjoyed fighting together, new blood. You deserve something good for your efforts. Worten, reward {mf|him|her}!"

traits.locale_text: « Bon, au moins, c'était une bonne chasse ! J'ai passé un bon moment à combattre à vos côtés, novice. Vous méritez un souvenir pour vos efforts. Worten, récompense-{mf|le|la} ! »

languages.text: 「まあ、狩りは楽しいものだったさ！それが続いている間はな！一緒に戦えて楽しかった。お前には、その努力に報いる記念品がふさわしい。ヴォルテン、報酬を！」
languages.original_text: "This has been a fine hunt! I have enjoyed fighting together, new blood. You deserve something good for your efforts. Worten, reward {mf|him|her}!"

traits.locale_text: 「まあ、狩りは楽しいものだったさ！それが続いている間はな！一緒に戦えて楽しかった。お前には、その努力に報いる記念品がふさわしい。ヴォルテン、報酬を！」

languages.text: "Das war eine gute Jagd! Es war eine Freude, an Eurer Seite zu kämpfen, neues Blut. Ihr verdient etwas Gutes für Eure Mühen. Worten, belohnt {mf|ihn|sie}!"
languages.original_text: "This has been a fine hunt! I have enjoyed fighting together, new blood. You deserve something good for your efforts. Worten, reward {mf|him|her}!"

traits.locale_text: "Nun, die Jagd hat Spaß gemacht! Es war eine Freude, an Eurer Seite zu kämpfen, neues Blut. Ihr verdient ein Souvenir für Eure Mühen. Worten, belohnt {mf|ihn|sie}!

languages.text: "Güzel bir av oldu! Birlikte dövüşmek hoşuma gitti taze kan. Çabaların karşılığında düzgün bir şeyleri hak ettin. Worten, ona ödülünü ver!"
languages.original_text: "This has been a fine hunt! I have enjoyed fighting together, new blood. You deserve something good for your efforts. Worten, reward {mf|him|her}!"
